## Session lesson — `65163901` (7 Jul 2026): happy path fixed, bug_122 not

Both scenarios were created **together**; happy path was corrected **turn by turn** with user logs; bug_122 **did not** inherit the same understanding.

### Chronology of failures (same session)

| When | What happened | Mistake |
|---|---|---|
| **Creation** | `bug_122` repro = missing proposal UI / logcat only | **Wrong symptom** — bug is **two Monica rows** on Louys contacts, not housing wizard empty |
| **Delivery fix** (user: invité trop tôt) | Sequential send → recipient in `_run_proposal_send_*` | Shared — OK for delivery order |
| **Happy path extended** | Accept + active hub (`_run_proposal_happy_path_once`) | `bug_122` still judged “clean” on delivery/hub, **not** duplicate contacts |
| **User: « applique les correctifs happy path sur bug_122 »** (16:07) | Ported accept + hub into `bug_122` | **Did not** re-read handshake pattern; **did not** add duplicate probe; parallel `inviter-standby` **unchanged** |
| **User saw 2× Monica on screen** | Attempts 1–2 classified **clean** | Sonde cherchait livraison/hub, pas doublons |
| **Duplicate probe v1** | Banner id only / wrong navigation | Still not **two occurrences** |
| **User: « Maestro ne compte qu’une occurrence »** | `invitee-assert` + probe without `index: 1` | **Second** comprehension failure on the **same** bug definition |
| **Late “cleanup”** | Removed redundant handshake asserts | **Kept parallel standby** — user later had to name this as the **main** happy-path fix that was never ported |

### What “apply happy path to bug_122” should have meant

After duplicate probe exists and bug is absent:

- `_connect_handshake_sequential` (not parallel standby)
- `_run_proposal_happy_path_once` for end state (or explicit probe-only scope from user)
- Same Maestro flows / logcat gates / scroll patterns as happy path
- **Clean** = `assert_no_duplicate` + happy path completion — not “Monica visible once”

### Promised vs delivered (do not repeat)

| Said / implied | Actually shipped (65163901) |
|---|---|
| bug_122 aligned with happy path | Delivery phases partially shared; handshake still parallel; repro criterion wrong for hours |
| Duplicate detection added | v1 missing; v2 inadequate (`visible` once); v3 only after user quote |
| Apply happy path fixes | Accept/hub copied; **sequential handshake not copied** until a later session |

